##############################################################
#
#  Setup
#
#

Context("Numeric");
#given
$we = random(20,40,1);

#computation
$m = $we/9.81;
$wm = $m*1.62;


#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.05,
tolType=>'relative');

##############################################################
#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

If scale measures an object's weight as [`[$we]`] [`N`] on earth [`(g_{earth}=9.81m/s^2)`], 
what weight would the same scale measure with the same object on the moon [`(g_{moon}=1.62m/s^2)`]?

[`W_{moon}=`] [______]{"$wm"} [`N`]

What is the object's mass in [`kg`]?

[`m = `] [______]{"$m"} [`kg`]

END_PGML

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

